					<description><![CDATA[Tích hợp Active Directory với Nutanix Community Edition Trong bài này mình sẽ hướng dẫn cách tích hợp chứng thực user cho giao diện quản lý PRISM thông qua Avtive directory Đăng nhập giao diện quản lý PRISM, click nút Settings và chọn Authentication Cick chọn New Directory Điền các tham số Active Directory vào <a class="more-link" href="./../../../tich-hop-active-directory-voi-nutanix-community-edition/index.html">Read More ...</a>]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a class="a2a_button_facebook" href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/facebook?linkurl=.%2F%2Ftich-hop-active-directory-voi-nutanix-community-edition%2F&amp;linkname=T%C3%ADch%20h%E1%BB%A3p%20Active%20Directory%20v%E1%BB%9Bi%20Nutanix%20Community%20Edition" title="Facebook" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a class="a2a_button_twitter" href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/twitter?linkurl=.%2F%2Ftich-hop-active-directory-voi-nutanix-community-edition%2F&amp;linkname=T%C3%ADch%20h%E1%BB%A3p%20Active%20Directory%20v%E1%BB%9Bi%20Nutanix%20Community%20Edition" title="Twitter" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a class="a2a_button_email" href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/email?linkurl=.%2F%2Ftich-hop-active-directory-voi-nutanix-community-edition%2F&amp;linkname=T%C3%ADch%20h%E1%BB%A3p%20Active%20Directory%20v%E1%BB%9Bi%20Nutanix%20Community%20Edition" title="Email" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a class="a2a_dd a2a_counter addtoany_share_save addtoany_share" href="https://www.addtoany.com/share#url=.%2F%2Ftich-hop-active-directory-voi-nutanix-community-edition%2F&#038;title=T%C3%ADch%20h%E1%BB%A3p%20Active%20Directory%20v%E1%BB%9Bi%20Nutanix%20Community%20Edition" data-a2a-url="./../../../tich-hop-active-directory-voi-nutanix-community-edition/index.html" data-a2a-title="Tích hợp Active Directory với Nutanix Community Edition"></a></p><p><span style="color: #0000ff;"><strong>Tích hợp Active Directory với Nutanix Community Edition</strong></span></p>
<p>Trong bài này mình sẽ hướng dẫn cách tích hợp chứng thực user cho giao diện quản lý PRISM thông qua Avtive directory</p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Nutanix-Integrate-AD-1.png" rel="lightbox[1481]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1482" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Nutanix-Integrate-AD-1-620x346.png" alt="Nutanix-Integrate-AD-1" width="620" height="346" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Nutanix-Integrate-AD-1-620x346.png 620w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Nutanix-Integrate-AD-1-920x514.png 920w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Nutanix-Integrate-AD-1.png 1334w" sizes="(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px" /></a></p>
<p>Đăng nhập giao diện quản lý PRISM, click nút <span style="text-decoration: underline;">Settings</span> và chọn <span style="text-decoration: underline;">Authentication</span></p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Nutanix-Integrate-AD-2.png" rel="lightbox[1481]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1483" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Nutanix-Integrate-AD-2-620x346.png" alt="Nutanix-Integrate-AD-2" width="620" height="346" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Nutanix-Integrate-AD-2-620x346.png 620w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Nutanix-Integrate-AD-2-920x514.png 920w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Nutanix-Integrate-AD-2.png 1334w" sizes="(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px" /></a></p>
<p>Cick chọn<span style="text-decoration: underline;"> New Directory</span></p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Nutanix-Integrate-AD-3.png" rel="lightbox[1481]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1484" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Nutanix-Integrate-AD-3-620x346.png" alt="Nutanix-Integrate-AD-3" width="620" height="346" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Nutanix-Integrate-AD-3-620x346.png 620w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Nutanix-Integrate-AD-3-920x514.png 920w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Nutanix-Integrate-AD-3.png 1334w" sizes="(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px" /></a></p>
<p>Điền các tham số Active Directory vào textbox tương ứng</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Name</span>: đặt tên sao cho dễ nhớ (không dùng dấu . vì sẽ báo lỗi)<br />
<span style="text-decoration: underline;">Domain</span>: tên domain của bạn, trong bài mình dùng domain active directory của mình là vmblogs.vn<br />
<span style="text-decoration: underline;">Directory URL</span>: đường dẫn trỏ đến active directory server<br />
<span style="text-decoration: underline;">Directory Type</span>: Active directory<br />
<span style="text-decoration: underline;">Connection Type</span>: LDAP</p>
<p>Click nút <span style="text-decoration: underline;">Save</span> để lưu các thiết lập</p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Nutanix-Integrate-AD-4.png" rel="lightbox[1481]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1485" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Nutanix-Integrate-AD-4-620x346.png" alt="Nutanix-Integrate-AD-4" width="620" height="346" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Nutanix-Integrate-AD-4-620x346.png 620w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Nutanix-Integrate-AD-4-920x514.png 920w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Nutanix-Integrate-AD-4.png 1334w" sizes="(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px" /></a></p>
<p>Click <span style="text-decoration: underline;">Close</span> để đóng hộp thoại</p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Nutanix-Integrate-AD-5.png" rel="lightbox[1481]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1486" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Nutanix-Integrate-AD-5-620x346.png" alt="Nutanix-Integrate-AD-5" width="620" height="346" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Nutanix-Integrate-AD-5-620x346.png 620w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Nutanix-Integrate-AD-5-920x514.png 920w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Nutanix-Integrate-AD-5.png 1334w" sizes="(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px" /></a></p>
<p>Tiếp tục chọn <span style="text-decoration: underline;">Settings</span> =&gt; <span style="text-decoration: underline;">Role Mapping</span></p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Nutanix-Integrate-AD-6.png" rel="lightbox[1481]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1487" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Nutanix-Integrate-AD-6-620x346.png" alt="Nutanix-Integrate-AD-6" width="620" height="346" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Nutanix-Integrate-AD-6-620x346.png 620w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Nutanix-Integrate-AD-6-920x514.png 920w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Nutanix-Integrate-AD-6.png 1334w" sizes="(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px" /></a></p>
<p>Click chọn <span style="text-decoration: underline;">New Mapping</span></p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Nutanix-Integrate-AD-7.png" rel="lightbox[1481]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1488" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Nutanix-Integrate-AD-7-620x346.png" alt="Nutanix-Integrate-AD-7" width="620" height="346" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Nutanix-Integrate-AD-7-620x346.png 620w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Nutanix-Integrate-AD-7-920x514.png 920w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Nutanix-Integrate-AD-7.png 1334w" sizes="(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px" /></a></p>
<p>Điền các thông số cần thiết</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Directory</span>: Chọn directory, do ở đây mình chỉ có 1 directory nên tự động được chọn sẵn<br />
<span style="text-decoration: underline;">LDAP type</span>: chọn loại đối tượng Active Directory để gán quyền, ở đây có thể tùy chọn User, Group hoặc OU<br />
<span style="text-decoration: underline;">Role</span>: có 3 Role để lựa chọn là Viewer (chỉ xem và theo dõi vận hành), User Admin hoặc Cluster Admin</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Value</span>: nhập đúng giá trị của LDAP type, trong ảnh là ví dụ mình tạo cho user nutanix1 quyền Viewer</p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Nutanix-Integrate-AD-8.png" rel="lightbox[1481]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1489" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Nutanix-Integrate-AD-8-620x346.png" alt="Nutanix-Integrate-AD-8" width="620" height="346" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Nutanix-Integrate-AD-8-620x346.png 620w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Nutanix-Integrate-AD-8-920x514.png 920w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Nutanix-Integrate-AD-8.png 1334w" sizes="(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px" /></a></p>
<p>Đăng nhập giao diện quản lý PRISM bằng tài khoản domain đã map ở phần trước</p>
<p>Cú pháp là <span style="text-decoration: underline;">user@domain</span></p>
<p>Ví dụ trong bài là <span style="text-decoration: underline;">nutanix1@vmblogs.vn</span></p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Nutanix-Integrate-AD-9.png" rel="lightbox[1481]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1490" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Nutanix-Integrate-AD-9-620x346.png" alt="Nutanix-Integrate-AD-9" width="620" height="346" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Nutanix-Integrate-AD-9-620x346.png 620w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Nutanix-Integrate-AD-9-920x514.png 920w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Nutanix-Integrate-AD-9.png 1334w" sizes="(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px" /></a></p>
<p>Đăng nhập thành công với user domain đã tạo</p>
<p>Chúc các bạn thành công</p>
<p><a class="a2a_button_facebook" href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/facebook?linkurl=.%2F%2Ftich-hop-active-directory-voi-nutanix-community-edition%2F&amp;linkname=T%C3%ADch%20h%E1%BB%A3p%20Active%20Directory%20v%E1%BB%9Bi%20Nutanix%20Community%20Edition" title="Facebook" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a class="a2a_button_twitter" href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/twitter?linkurl=.%2F%2Ftich-hop-active-directory-voi-nutanix-community-edition%2F&amp;linkname=T%C3%ADch%20h%E1%BB%A3p%20Active%20Directory%20v%E1%BB%9Bi%20Nutanix%20Community%20Edition" title="Twitter" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a class="a2a_button_email" href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/email?linkurl=.%2F%2Ftich-hop-active-directory-voi-nutanix-community-edition%2F&amp;linkname=T%C3%ADch%20h%E1%BB%A3p%20Active%20Directory%20v%E1%BB%9Bi%20Nutanix%20Community%20Edition" title="Email" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a class="a2a_dd a2a_counter addtoany_share_save addtoany_share" href="https://www.addtoany.com/share#url=.%2F%2Ftich-hop-active-directory-voi-nutanix-community-edition%2F&#038;title=T%C3%ADch%20h%E1%BB%A3p%20Active%20Directory%20v%E1%BB%9Bi%20Nutanix%20Community%20Edition" data-a2a-url="./../../../tich-hop-active-directory-voi-nutanix-community-edition/index.html" data-a2a-title="Tích hợp Active Directory với Nutanix Community Edition"></a></p>]]></content:encoded>
					
